          .container
            .row
              .col-lg-4
                img.wow.bounceInLeft.img-responsive(src='/static/img/subheadshot.jpg', alt='Brett Oberg headshot')
              .col-lg-8.wow.bounceInRight
                h2.section-heading Brett Oberg              
                h4.light UI Designer & Developer
                |                     
                p I am a student studying Information Systems, Operations Management, and Computer Science at the University of Wisconsin - Madison. Professionally, I am interested in software development, UI/UX design, web development, and entrepreurship. I have 5 years of general work experience, and for the past 3 years, I have been working to develop these skills:
                  ul
                    li Web Development: 3 years
                    li Mobile Development: 2 years
                    li UI/UX Development: 1 years
                p If you are interested in reviewing my work please visit my #[a(href='https://github.com/bjoberg') GitHub page].
                p Personally, I am a very active person interested in: golf, running, working out, listening to music, and traveling.
                p Thanks for taking the time to visit this site. If you have concerns, advice, or just want someone to discuss design techniques with, please reach out to me. I am always looking to speak with new people.
                a.mdl-button.mdl-button--accent.mdl-js-button.mdl-button--raised.mdl-js-ripple-effect(href='http://brettoberg.com/documents/BrettOberg-Resume.pdf') Resume
