        section.bg-primary
          .container      
          .container
            .row
              .col-lg-3.col-md-6.text-center
                .service-box
                  i.fa.fa-4x.fa-desktop.wow.bounceIn
                  |                         
                  h3 Web
                  |                         
                  p Web design / programming is what I like to do, and what I excel at. Focused on clean, responsive design, I believe that the first step in good web design is the ability to view a site on all devices. I want to contribute to the growth of the internet by designing beautiful websites for everyone to enjoy.
              |                 
              .col-lg-3.col-md-6.text-center
                .service-box
                  i.fa.fa-4x.fa-mobile.wow.bounceIn(data-wow-delay='.1s')
                  |                         
                  h3 iOS
                  |                         
                  p iOS development has always been an interest of mine. Ever since I bought my first iPhone, I have always wanted to make applications that ran in my hand. I have not released any applications to the App Store, but I have dozens of private apps that I have developed for my own personal use.
              |                 
              .col-lg-3.col-md-6.text-center
                .service-box
                  i.fa.fa-4x.fa-android.wow.bounceIn(data-wow-delay='.2s')
                  |                         
                  h3 Android
                  |                         
                  p Development for Android devices has been a recent interest of mine. Onset by my work with the UW Athletic Department, I have become fascinated by Google's material design pattern and the community of developers working with Android devices.
              |                 
              .col-lg-3.col-md-6.text-center
                .service-box
                  i.fa.fa-4x.fa-server.wow.bounceIn(data-wow-delay='.3s')
                  |                         
                  h3 Services
                  |                         
                  p Backend development is my weakest skill. Launching my own website has forced me to learn basic server management and manipulation. I hope to continue growing this skill as my web, iOS, and Android development / design expands.
        |     
